						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription. It registers the gift as tax-free <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna</hi> the village(,) Nariyār-ēndal for the requirements of offerings and unguents to god Tāntōṉṟi-Āḷuḍaiya-nāyaṉār at Śaṇbai <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīrarājēndraśōḻapuram in Vāṇagappāḍināḍu on the northern bank.</p>						

