<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi> koṉeriṉmelko
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṇṭāṉ tirupuvaṉac cakkaravattika
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> cuntarapāṇṭiya tevaṟku yā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇṭu Eṭṭāvatu peṇṇai vaṭakarai
<lb n="5"/>vāṇakoppāṭi nāṭṭu caṇpaiyā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉa virarācentira (centira) coḻapurat
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tu Uṭaiyār tiruttāntoṉṟi Āḷu
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>ṭai</unclear>ya nāyaṉār tevatāṉam mutalaṭaṅka
<lb n="9"/>Iṟaiyiliyāka Amutupaṭikkum (mm) veñ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>caṉattukkum tirumeṟpūccuk
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kkum tevatāṉa mutalaṭaṅka Iṟai
<lb n="12" break="no"/>yiliyāka viṭṭa nariyārental
<lb n="13"/>kiḻpāṟkellai Atti Ental te
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nkaraikku meṟku vāṇakappāṭi E
<lb n="15" break="no"/>llaikku kiḻakku caṇpai Ellaik
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ku vaṭakku kalloṭṭukku Ellai<note n="68-*">Stops here.</note>
</p>

